{"type": "article", "id": 21222, "title": "流线型的洗手池", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-25T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110557MXFWwpeViLd8YtSu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套很有流动感的卫浴设计，来自匈牙利布达佩斯的设计师 Kovacs Apor。洗手池的凹槽也没有前后的遮挡，像是一个人坐在了圆筒上，储存空间分布在左右两端，可替换以木质材料，也是将杂物隐藏起来，是极简的设计。几个洗手池并排在一起可以组成流动的线条，它目前还是一个概念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508416BYZLkfzUJsHipd1.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"292\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.27809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150842d0XJtIA27bwjfNTx.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508429kQt73HKfIGhjXNP.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"331\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.3152381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150843Ckl1YawsGWoeNEyg.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}